    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Escape should be done with <code>\\</code>, not <code>/</code>.</p>\n\n<p>So <code>r.append('\\n');</code> or <code>r.append(\"\\n\");</code> will work (<code>StringBuilder</code> has overloaded methods for <code>char</code> and <code>String</code> type).</p>\n"
